SAMPLE_add_point_to_line = {
	# Adds a random point to the line graph
	# This count is displayed as an x-axis label, increment it
	add_to_variable = {
		SAMPLE_count = 1
	}
	# We keep track of the last y position so we can calculate the slope
	set_variable = {
		SAMPLE_last_y_position_green = SAMPLE_y_position_green
	}
	set_variable = {
		SAMPLE_last_y_position_red = SAMPLE_y_position_red
	}

	# The y position offset is the inverse of the y position
	set_temp_variable = {
		offset_green = SAMPLE_last_y_position_green
	}
	set_temp_variable = {
		offset_red = SAMPLE_last_y_position_red
	}
	set_temp_variable = {
		offset_light_red = SAMPLE_last_y_position_light_red
	}
	set_temp_variable = {
		offset_blue = SAMPLE_last_y_position_blue
	}
	set_temp_variable = {
		offset_light_blue = SAMPLE_last_y_position_light_blue
	}
	set_temp_variable = {
		offset_grey = SAMPLE_last_y_position_grey
	}
	set_temp_variable = {
		offset_light_white = SAMPLE_last_y_position_light_white
	}
	set_temp_variable = {
		offset_red = SAMPLE_last_y_position_red
	}
	multiply_temp_variable = {
		offset_green = -1
	}
	multiply_temp_variable = {
		offset_red = -1
	}
	multiply_temp_variable = {
		offset_light_red = -1
	}
	multiply_temp_variable = {
		offset_blue = -1
	}
	multiply_temp_variable = {
		offset_light_blue = -1
	}
	multiply_temp_variable = {
		offset_light_white = -1
	}
	multiply_temp_variable = {
		offset_grey = -1
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_offsets_green = offset_green
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_offsets_red = offset_red
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_offsets_light_red = offset_light_red
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_offsets_blue = offset_blue
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_offsets_light_blue = offset_light_blue
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_offsets_light_white = offset_light_white
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_offsets_grey = offset_grey
	}
	# The 'slope' here is simply the difference between the current y value and the last one, divided by 2 plus 50
	# These last two changes are needed for the shader
	set_temp_variable = {
		diff_green = SAMPLE_y_position_green
	}
	subtract_from_temp_variable = {
		diff_green = SAMPLE_last_y_position_green
	}
	divide_temp_variable = {
		diff_green = 2
	}
	add_to_temp_variable = {
		diff_green = 50
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_slopes_green = diff_green
	}

	set_temp_variable = {
		diff_red = SAMPLE_y_position_red
	}
	subtract_from_temp_variable = {
		diff_red = SAMPLE_last_y_position_red
	}
	divide_temp_variable = {
		diff_red = 2
	}
	add_to_temp_variable = {
		diff_red = 50
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_slopes_red = diff_red
	}

	set_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_red = SAMPLE_y_position_light_red
	}
	subtract_from_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_red = SAMPLE_last_y_position_light_red
	}
	divide_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_red = 2
	}
	add_to_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_red = 50
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_slopes_light_red = diff_light_red
	}

	set_temp_variable = {
		diff_blue = SAMPLE_y_position_blue
	}
	subtract_from_temp_variable = {
		diff_blue = SAMPLE_last_y_position_blue
	}
	divide_temp_variable = {
		diff_blue = 2
	}
	add_to_temp_variable = {
		diff_blue = 50
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_slopes_blue = diff_blue
	}

	set_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_blue = SAMPLE_y_position_light_blue
	}
	subtract_from_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_blue = SAMPLE_last_y_position_light_blue
	}
	divide_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_blue = 2
	}
	add_to_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_blue = 50
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_slopes_light_blue = diff_light_blue
	}

	set_temp_variable = {
		diff_light_white = SAMPLE_y_position_light_white
	}
	subtract_from_temp_variable = {

	set_temp_variable = {

	}
	subtract_from_temp_variable = {

	}
	divide_temp_variable = {
		diff_grey = 2
	}
	add_to_temp_variable = {
		diff_grey = 50
	}
	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_graph_slopes_grey = diff_grey
	}

	add_to_array = {
		SAMPLE_numbers = SAMPLE_count
	}

	set_global_flag = { flag = graph_cooldown value = 1 days = 20 }
}
